OL,3,CAlmost a third of Londoners say the
OL,4,Ccapital is unsuitable to raise a child
OL,6,FAlmost a third of Londoners consider
OL,7,Fthe capital an unsuitable place to
OL,8,Fraise children. The amount of children
OL,9,Fliving in the city is declining at a
OL,10,Ffaster rate than anywhere else in the
OL,11,FUK.
OL,13,FThis is according to a new report by
OL,14,Fthe Economy, Culture and Skills
OL,15,Fcommittee which the London Assembly is
OL,16,Flaunching today.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
