OL,3,CAlmost a third of Londoners say the
OL,4,Ccapital is unsuitable to raise a child
OL,6,FFamilies face significant challenges
OL,7,Fincluding the availability and
OL,8,Faffordability of housing, childcare,
OL,9,Fand child-friendly neighbourhoods that
OL,10,Fallow children and families to thrive.
OL,12,FCosts of nurseries in London are the
OL,13,Fhighest in England- followed closely
OL,14,Fby outer London. The weekly price of a
OL,15,Ffull-time nursery place for a toddler
OL,16,Fwas 34% higher than the national
OL,17,Faverage.
OL,19,FKatherine Hill the Strategic Programme
OL,20,FManager said:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
