CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1772917925
OL,3,CAlmost a third of Londoners say the
OL,4,Ccapital is unsuitable to raise a child
OL,6,F""It is very clear that the costs (of
OL,7,Fchildcare) in London are extremely
OL,8,Fhigh, and lots of people talk in terms
OL,9,Fof it equalling a second mortgage or
OL,10,Fthose sorts of figures."
OL,12,FLondon's attitude towards children's
OL,13,Fplay is also an issue faced by
OL,14,Ffamilies in London.
OL,16,FOne parent in West London explained
OL,17,Fhow her family was drawn to their
OL,18,Fcurrent home because of the communal
OL,19,Fgarden it offered but two years ago,
OL,20,Fball games were banned. She said:
OL,26,@nD@BOUnD@cpmoD@Jpn
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
