FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1772917925
OL,3,CAlmost a third of Londoners say the
OL,4,Ccapital is unsuitable to raise a child
OL,6,F"Children's everyday freedom to play
OL,7,Fin our community came to an end, when
OL,8,FEstate Management installed No Ball
OL,9,FGames signs around our communal garden
OL,10,Fspace, without notice, consultation,
OL,11,For explanation."
OL,13,FShe says her family considered moving,
OL,14,Fas they felt that their children were
OL,15,F"no longer welcome".
OL,17,FThe report suggests that many parents
OL,18,Ffavour leafier suburbs over the city.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@PO]
