OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1772917925
OL,3,CAlmost a third of Londoners say the
OL,4,Ccapital is unsuitable to raise a child
OL,6,FWhen choosing a place to live, most
OL,7,Fimportant factors were schools, crime
OL,8,Fand safety and being closer to family.
OL,10,FThe report, 'A London for every child:
OL,11,FReversing the city's declining child
OL,12,Fpopulation' sets out steps for the
OL,13,FMayor to make London a child-friendly
OL,14,Fcity.
OL,16,FIt has called on the Mayor to act in
OL,17,Ffive key areas:
OL,19,FThe committee is launching the report
OL,20,Fat a primary school in Camden this
OL,21,Fmorning.
